Articles.Content:
Im currently using the opt parts a lot along with the mk 2 parts but im trying to build a vtol spaceplane but all the vtols i know about are all atmospheric which as we all know wont work on the Mun and other moons an planets.

So if anyone knows of a mod or is currently making a mod with a vacuum vtol please let me know.

Thank You
USI Freight Transport Technologies, for one.
